I"2<p>We are a dynamic research group at the <a href="https://life-sciences.biu.ac.il/en">Bar-Ilan University School of Life Sciences</a>. Our aim is to explore and understand <a href="http://condensedconcepts.blogspot.nl/2013/05/what-is-quantum-matter.html">Diet-Microbiome-Host interactions</a>, including strange metals, high-temperature superconductors, and quantum critical electron matter.</p>

